DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: I recognise you from the wanted posters!
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: I recognise you from the wanted posters!

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?

Message.SourceString: Oh, don't mind me here. I'm just enjoying the architecture. I'll meet you at Bramblemead Village if you want to chat.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, don't mind me here. I'm just enjoying the architecture. I'll meet you at Bramblemead Village if you want to chat.

Message.SourceString: Oh, don't mind me here. I'm just enjoying the architecture. I'll meet you at Bramblemead Village if you want to chat.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, don't mind me here. I'm just enjoying the architecture. I'll meet you at Bramblemead Village if you want to chat.

Message.SourceString: We can relax for a little while, but not forever. Velgar was one tough cookie, but he's just the foot soldier. Queen Kuldra is out there somewhere and she won't sit quietly for long.
Message.LocalizedString: We can relax for a little while, but not forever. Velgar was one tough cookie, but he's just the foot soldier. Queen Kuldra is out there somewhere and she won't sit quietly for long.

Message.SourceString: Aren't you helping the others out? What are you talking to me for? Check your map if you're not sure what you're meant to be doing.
Message.LocalizedString: Aren't you helping the others out? What are you talking to me for? Check your map if you're not sure what you're meant to be doing.

Message.SourceString: Oh, the cruelty of time, erasing even our deeds. I was once a famous and adored hero. Now everyone just calls me "that wise old man". Rude really.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, the cruelty of time, erasing even our deeds. I was once a famous and adored hero. Now everyone just calls me "that wise old man". Rude really.

Message.SourceString: A lifetime of heroism, and no recognition. But you rob one bank, and suddenly everyone knows your name!
Message.LocalizedString: A lifetime of heroism, and no recognition. But you rob one bank, and suddenly everyone knows your name!

Message.SourceString: We've not been here that long, but I can tell you that Ashenfall is special. You must feel it? Magic everywhere?
Message.LocalizedString: We've not been here that long, but I can tell you that Ashenfall is special. You must feel it? Magic everywhere?

Message.SourceString: The whole continent feels like its infused with anima. Literally pouring out of the ground in some places. That's just not normal.
Message.LocalizedString: The whole continent feels like its infused with anima. Literally pouring out of the ground in some places. That's just not normal.

Message.SourceString: Probably goes someway to explaining the enormous dragon that wants to kill us... along with all the other things that want to kill us.
Message.LocalizedString: Probably goes someway to explaining the enormous dragon that wants to kill us... along with all the other things that want to kill us.
